description.alternacraft.aio_axe:
Auto-Smelts!
Puts drops directly in inventory.
Poisons your enemies.
Blinds your enemies and slows them down.
description.alternacraft.aio_boots: Prevents fall damage and grants strength 2, regeneration 2 and fire resistance when full set is worn.
description.alternacraft.aio_chestplate: Prevents fall damage and grants strength 2, regeneration 2 and fire resistance when full set is worn.

description.alternacraft.aio_pickaxe:
Auto-Smelts!
Puts drops directly in inventory.
Rightclick to put down mining lights.
Shift Rightclick with an ore in your offhand to find the distance of the ore using sonar.
description.alternacraft.aio_scythe:
Auto-Smelts!
Puts drops directly in inventory.
Automatically replants harvested crops (rightclick).
Tills a 3x3
description.alternacraft.aio_shovel:
Auto-Smelts!
Puts drops directly in inventory.
Gives xp for every block mined.
Mines a 3x3.
description.alternacraft.aio_sword:
Sets the enemy on fire.
Puts drops directly in inventory.
Poisons your enemies with an extra large swing.
Blinds your enemies.
